# 🎲 Dice Roller (Python)

A simple console-based dice rolling simulator written in Python.  
The program randomly generates dice rolls, displays them using ASCII art, and calculates the total result.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Roll from 1 to 6 dice per turn  
- Random results using Python’s `random` module  
- Clean ASCII art visualization of dice  
- Input validation and replay option (`y/n`)  
- Clear total score display after each roll  

---

